{"tid":541165,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公共圖書館大手購「歌共書」","createTime":"2018-01-26T07:05:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-26T08:30:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e5445d7abc125c1f06e31a7b09fe2f49e2c8c13f","tid":541165,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:05:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180126/20286111\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180126%2F20286111&d=1VqxJALpQ4PnxmeZzgJjrhxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=0011f08e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180126%2F20286111&h=7a2bb599\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180126/20286111</a><br />\n<br />\n公共圖書館大手購「歌共書」<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180126/large/1223kaho2005.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180126%2Flarge%2F1223kaho2005.jpg&h=6d4e7a21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港公共圖書館也有大量中共力推的《習近平談治國理政》可供借閱。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】除了三聯、中華、商務印書館3間本港主要書店，連香港公共圖書館也有大量中共力推的《習近平談治國理政》可供借閱。根據香港公共圖書館網上圖書目錄，該書有多達45本存貨，分佈於全港各區的公共圖書館。以書本在市面以128元售計算，康文署共花費納稅人4,864元來購入該批書籍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n題材包括一帶一路<br />\n<br />\n除了《習近平談治國理政》，香港公共圖書館亦有35本習近平的演講著作、《讀懂中國外交戰略：中國國家主席習近平在國外訪問期間發表重要演講選讀》供借閱。針對近年中國積極推銷一帶一路，圖書館更備有繁、簡體字一帶一路著作供外借，如一帶一路發展聯會出版的《踏上一帶一路的時代巨輪》，全港備有45本，藏書量甚豐。<br />\n<br />\n本報向香港公共圖書館查詢《習近平談治國理政》借閱本為採購抑或贈本、採購原因等，康文署回覆指，《習近平談治國理政》的採購數量為38本，又指採購書籍時考慮整體館藏情況及發展方向、使用者的需求和興趣等因素，並無正面回應為何購買此書。<br />\n<br />\n■記者廖梓霖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n\t寫手封筆　銷量差「禁書」銳減<br />\n要聞 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t內地客︰大陸幾乎每人都買<br />\n要聞 3小時前<br />\n<br />\n\t主流書店一片紅　三中商力谷習「巨著」文化界︰西環決定你睇乜嘢書<br />\n要聞 3小時前"},{"pid":"1ae09a7df2ab9ab8456d7cefe0a6bf65717fc71a","tid":541165,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:24:24.000Z","msg":"我認為，老夫子既借閱率仲高D"},{"pid":"196c29b6045b2430b67068e9b76ae50b8c890a08","tid":541165,"uid":47259,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:25:49.000Z","msg":"買垃圾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77cea28edc283affa70c0f6743f82948ee6cd7fe","tid":541165,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ae09a7df2ab9ab8456d7cefe0a6bf65717fc71a","tid":541165,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:24:24.000Z","msg":"我認為，老夫子既借閱率仲高D"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:29:02.000Z","msg":"錯, 係叮噹/多啦A夢!"},{"pid":"23a1c200bd8d97897cdd1aab51b0c9370e2684a8","tid":541165,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.zxhsd.com/photo/book_b//C/02203/3496413-fm-b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.zxhsd.com%2Fphoto%2Fbook_b%2F%2FC%2F02203%2F3496413-fm-b.jpg&h=bf847c87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img3.jarhu.com/goodimages/201604/231/gi1461391388895.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg3.jarhu.com%2Fgoodimages%2F201604%2F231%2Fgi1461391388895.jpg&h=55d2ab33&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9bd5e09c803c3a050b81ec24eaeee3e01f7a494b","tid":541165,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:32:05.000Z","msg":"買多啲閃令令旅遊書都好過呢本垃圾啦。<br />\n<br />\n雖然大家都係垃圾。"},{"pid":"a4475997459ab5a4bc45e0a177d4806f73e9e57e","tid":541165,"uid":41508,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T07:33:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dde0c1cc4c727828935c022cda05932333354ce7","tid":541165,"uid":92301,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-26T08:30:08.000